00:34:16,380 --> 00:34:18,100
 Sorry, I've gotta get out of the university, right?

718
00:34:18,100 --> 00:34:22,980
 But anyway, homework number three is tomorrow,

719
00:34:22,980 --> 00:34:27,580
 when you go in, before you go in, so that would be today,

720
00:34:27,580 --> 00:34:29,420
 if we live by the Spirit,

721
00:34:29,420 --> 00:34:32,580
 let us keep in step with the Spirit, memorize it.

